                   queue.append((nr, nc))\n```\n\nThis solution uses a breadth-first search (BFS) approach starting from each gate (cells with value `0`). It explores all four possible directions (up, down, left, right) from each gate and updates the distance to the nearest gate for each empty room (cells with value `2147483647`). The BFS ensures that each room is updated with the shortest distance to a gate.", "estimated_date": 1438905600000}